Achievements.Name: Green around the Ears
Achievements.Description: Complete the entire game on Amateur.

Achievements.Name: Normal Is Good
Achievements.Description: Complete the entire game on Normal.

Achievements.Name: Back in My Day
Achievements.Description: Complete the entire game on Veteran.

Achievements.Name: Leave It to the Pro
Achievements.Description: Complete the entire game on Professional.

Achievements.Name: Mad Skillz
Achievements.Description: Max out all the skills that allow you to level up.

Achievements.Name: Silent Killer
Achievements.Description: Use a stealth attack to take down five enemies.

Achievements.Name: Finish What You Start
Achievements.Description: Perform a coup de grce on ten enemies.

Achievements.Name: Bob and Weave
Achievements.Description: Counter an enemy's attack three times in row.

Achievements.Name: Down, Not Out
Achievements.Description: Defeat an enemy while dying, then recover without any help.

Achievements.Name: Lifesaver
Achievements.Description: Help or rescue your partner ten times.

Achievements.Name: Weapons Master
Achievements.Description: Use all the weapons in the game and kill ten enemies with each of them.

Achievements.Name: Give a Little Push
Achievements.Description: Knock ten enemies off a high place.

Achievements.Name: Stuntman
Achievements.Description: Defeat 20 enemies with the Hydra using a quick shot.

Achievements.Name: Bring the Heat
Achievements.Description: Take down an enemy from 50 meters away with a headshot using the thermal scope.

Achievements.Name: High Voltage
Achievements.Description: Defeat ten enemies with a stun rod charge attack.

Achievements.Name: B.O.W.s Are Ugly
Achievements.Description: Defeat 100 enemies that have come out of a chrysalid.

Achievements.Name: I Prefer Them Alive
Achievements.Description: Rescue two female survivors at the cathedral.

Achievements.Name: Flying Ace
Achievements.Description: Pilot the VTOL without getting a scratch on it.

Achievements.Name: Hard Choice
Achievements.Description: Shoot the helicopter pilot with a Magnum at point-blank range.

Achievements.Name: Sneaking Around
Achievements.Description: Get through the aircraft carrier's bridge area without being noticed.
